<p class=\"showTitle\">Junta Juleil 10th Anniversary</p>
<p>Junta Juleil Productions celebrates its 10th Anniversary with a smorgasbord of film, live performance, and rare, never-before-seen archival material. Featuring works described as \"dystopian metatheatrical fantasia\" (Time Out New York on Dreams of the Clockmaker), \"like a 1980s Judith Krantz bestseller getting the Wes Craven treatment\" (Flavorpill on Stage Blood is Never Enough), and \"captivating, with a vision and creative flair very much their own\" (The New York Theater Review on Sean Gill\'s films).</p>
<p>Trailer: <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/80744103\" target=\"blank\">https://vimeo.com/80744103</a><br/>
			Website: <a href=\"http://www.seangillfilms.com\" target=\"blank\">www.seangillfilms.com</a></p>
